Bain Capital LP: Company Profile - Bloomberg




































































  









Feedback
























bain capital lp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Companies
Bain Capital, LP operates as an investment holding company. The Company provides private equity, public equity, fixed income and credit, venture capital, and other investment services. Bain Capital offers its services worldwide.




Corporate Information
Address:

200 Clarendon Street
Boston, MA 02116
United States


