Bain Capital Private Equity









⋮

Private Equity
Credit
Ventures
Public Equity



 




 











healthcare





healthcare Bain Capital Private Equity is one of the leading investors in the Healthcare sector.  Our global platform allows us to identify industry best-practices and help companies compete on a global scale, while our significant local presence provides insight into unique local markets.  Our deep historical experience in this space includes investments in hospitals, pharmaceuticals, medical products manufacturers, distributors and service providers.  Our extensive experience across the healthcare value chain allows us to better and more rapidly understand and support our management teams in the face of the key trends affecting the sector.





 

 

 

 






Related Team
Current Portfolio
Case Studies
 
 







Back 






Waters






 





Regions:


Industry:
healthcare 

Year:
1994 
Bain Capital acquired Waters, a manufacturer of liquid chromatography instruments for the pharmaceutical and life science industries, in 1994. An industry leader with a large installed instrument base, broad product suite and strong global presence, Bain Capital saw an opportunity to partner with management to improve the Waters’ performance and drive continued global expansion opportunities.
Bain Capital partnered with management to carve out Waters as a standalone entity from Milipore Corporation, investing in research and development and the acquisition of Acquired Phase Separations Limited to complement Waters’ existing consumable product portfolio. Following continued product development and performance improvement in the United States and abroad, including an 8% increase in sales and an 85% increase in earnings during the first year of ownership, the company went public in 1995.




Case studies are not intended to be illustrative for investment purposes and should not be relied upon for investment decision making.
This should not be considered an offer or solicitation of securities or investment services. Information is for informational purposes
only and intended for Management teams considering partnering with Bain Capital Partners.




 

































